content:
Prepare to assemble your loved parts into your own unique rockets!

RocKetApe is a collection of 10,000 customizable rockets assembled by hundreds of components.

Each time when you mint, you will receive rocket components enough for assembling one rocket. Once your unique rocket is confirmed, it will be permanently registered on the Etherum Blockchain.

Our website: https://rocketape.club/
Our Twitter: https://twitter.com/ape_ket
